### for github serach for terms in in a specific repo's issues
```bash
# genrel syntax
repo:owner/repo-name is:issue <search-term>

# real
repo:hashicorp/terraform-provider-awscc is:issue chatbot

# search with issues in title
is:issue is:open in:title "default tags" 
```


### Search terms to find good repos
```bash
# search in github for these terms
<technology> deployment example
<technology> web application example
<technology> web server example
<technology> microservice example
<technology> full stack example
<technology> <combine with any other terms above or not> docker compose
<technology> ci/cd
<technology> serverless
<technology> PWA or SPA
<technology> demo
<technology> kubernetes
```


